*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /'bɒtən/

===Adjective===
'''boughten'''

# {{archaic}} Characterized as having been purchased or [[bought]] versus handmade.  Found regionally in the US and other English-speaking communities.
#: ''Is that a '''boughten''' chair?''

